                            Consistency
                        

                            Providing you with a Value investment approach that utilizes 
                            in-house research, rather than market emotions or a herd mentality, 
                            to help you avoid the pitfalls that can be detrimental to long-term success.
                        








                            Discipline
                        

                            We are devoted to our core values, thinking independently 
                            of the Wall Street crowd and executing investment decisions 
                            that seek to enhance the odds of outstanding risk-adjusted returns.
                        





                            Integrity
                        

                            We strive to earn your loyalty and trust through 
                            personalized service, transparent communication, 
                            and execution of our value-oriented investment process.
                        











What we do 


                        We believe that a value approach to investing will prevail over other styles in the long run. We use a disciplined methodology to evaluate businesses, which enables us to think independently of the Wall Street crowd.
                    










